   "source": [
    "## Summary\n",
    "\n",
    "This notebook covered:\n",
    "\n",
    "1. **LoRA Merging**: Combine adapter with base model\n",
    "2. **Quantization**: AWQ 4-bit size comparison\n",
    "3. **FastAPI Server**: Production-ready inference API\n",
    "4. **Streaming**: Token-by-token generation\n",
    "5. **vLLM Setup**: High-throughput serving configuration\n",
    "\n",
    "### Key Takeaways:\n",
    "\n",
    "- Merge LoRA adapters before deployment for efficiency\n",
    "- Quantization reduces model size 4× with minimal quality loss\n",
    "- vLLM provides 2-4× throughput vs. naive serving\n",
    "- Streaming improves user experience for long generations\n",
    "- Monitor latency and throughput in production"
   ]
  }
